@startuml State Diagram - Video Processing

title State Diagram - Video Lifecycle

[*] --> Uploaded : User uploads video

Uploaded --> Processing : Save to storage\nCreate DB record

state Processing {
  [*] --> DownloadingFromStorage
  DownloadingFromStorage --> PreparingForAI : Download complete
  PreparingForAI --> SendingToAI : Save to temp file
  SendingToAI --> AnalyzingVideo : POST /predict
  AnalyzingVideo --> ReceivingResults : AI processes chunks
  ReceivingResults --> [*] : Results received
}

Processing --> Completed : Prediction success\nUpdate DB
Processing --> Failed : Error occurred\nUpdate DB

Completed --> ViewingResults : User views video
ViewingResults --> GeneratingReport : User requests AI report
GeneratingReport --> ViewingResults : Report generated

Failed --> Retrying : Manual retry
Retrying --> Processing : Retry processing

Completed --> Deleted : User deletes video
Failed --> Deleted : User deletes video

Deleted --> [*]

@enduml

