title Entity Relationship Diagram - Database Schema

' Define entities
entity "User" as user {
  * _id : ObjectId <<PK>>
  --
  * email : String <<unique>>
  * name : String
  * phone : String <<unique>>
  * password : String
  photo : String
  * role : Enum('admin', 'user')
  totalPdf : Number
