' Relationships
user ||--o{ video : "owns (0..many)"

note right of video
  **Status Flow:**
  processing → completed
  processing → failed
  
  **Prediction JSON Structure:**
  {
    predictions: [...],
    summary: {...},
    video_info: {...}
  }
end note

note left of user
  **Password:** Hashed with bcrypt
  **Role:** Default is 'user'
  **Authentication:** 
  - Firebase Auth
  - JWT tokens
end note

